            What is covid-19?<br>
            What do I do if I have covid-19?<br>
            What are the symptoms of covid-19?<br>
            Where can I get tested for covid-19?<br>
            How is the coronavirus spread?<br>
            How do I protect myself against covid-19?<br>
            How many covid-19 cases are there in Barbados?<br>
            How long does covid-19 stay in your system?<br>
            What vaccines are available to counter covid-19?<br>
            What are the side effects of the covid-19 vaccines?<br>
            Where can I get vaccinated?<br>
            Why do I need the covid-19 vaccine?<br>
            Who should take the covid-19 vaccine?<br>
            Who should not take the covid-19 vaccine?<br>
            When am I fully vaccinated?<br>
            How long does the vaccine protect me against covid-19?
